message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.CY. The paper discusses natural language research and evaluation, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of automatic metrics and human judgments also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The discussion of human judgments and their difficulties in measurement suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and possibly cybernetics (cs.CY).
